<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <meta name="description" content="<%= description %>" />

    <!-- Favicon -->
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="/favicon/apple-touch-icon.png" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/favicon/favicon-32x32.png" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="/favicon/favicon-16x16.png" />
    <link rel="manifest" href="/favicon/site.webmanifest" />

    <!-- CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/output.css" />

    <!-- Font Awesome -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.2/css/all.min.css" />
  </head>
  <body class="flex flex-col min-h-screen bg-gray-50">
    <!-- Header -->
    <header><%- include('partials/header') %></header>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <main class="flex-grow">
      <!-- Page Title Section -->
      <section class="bg-gray-100 py-12">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
          <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 text-center">Professional Roofing Services</h1>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Content Section -->
      <section class="py-12">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nullam in dui mauris. Vivamus hendrerit arcu sed erat molestie vehicula. Sed auctor neque eu tellus rhoncus ut eleifend nibh
            porttitor.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
            Ut in nulla enim. Phasellus molestie magna non est bibendum non venenatis nisl tempor. Suspendisse dictum feugiat nisl ut dapibus. Mauris iaculis porttitor posuere.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="bg-gray-800 text-white py-8 mt-10"><%- include('partials/footer') %></footer>

    <!-- JavaScript -->
    <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
